{"tid":2075810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登拒絕川普額外一場總統大選辯論的要求 指只會進行3場大選辯論","createTime":"2020-06-23T05:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:38:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2fe4f18c1d90c33c1f3a212334fc5319ffbb8c","tid":2075810,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"最新更新：2020/06/23 13:05<br />\n（中央社華盛頓22日綜合外電報導）美國前副總統拜登（Joe Biden）篤定獲得民主黨提名競選總統，他的陣營今天允諾與對手、現任總統川普進行3場總統候選人電視辯論、1場副手辯論，但拒絕對方要求增加場次。<br />\n<br />\n「華爾街日報」報導，拜登陣營在致函「總統辯論委員會」（CPD）的信裡表示，他們接受原訂於9月、10月舉辦的辯論期程，並明確拒絕共和黨川普陣營想爭取額外再增1場總統候選人辯論。<br />\n<br />\n拜登陣營的競選總幹事狄倫（Jen O'Malley Dillon）在信中寫道：「川普陣營想再詳細協商的提議，無非只是想迴避公平、公正的辯論。」<br />\n<br />\n川普的幕僚上週促請辯論委員會額外加辦一場辯論，且時間應排在9月初，他們的說法是預期今年會有更多選民提早投票；川普陣營還施壓委員會，要讓雙方陣營能置喙辯論主持人的人選。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006230135.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202006230135.aspx&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7rPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=6375865c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006230135.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"a6cf4d72f8e1a2c7b9c65256680618ea46c47b74","tid":2075810,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"China Joe傀儡到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ced0f5569f5184cad66c21e60894528b6ccc8a","tid":2075810,"uid":82359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"Sleepy joe 驚輸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedbdfd4deba0a38a46266f89fb9d75318635a94","tid":2075810,"uid":231908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"訓係度贏"},{"pid":"f86f1ea9a8de35e3efa34fc32f7997f8e523b870","tid":2075810,"uid":4243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ced